ith immunosuppressive or myelosuppressive agents should be avoided if possible.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/65020/', '', 'Golimumab, Cyclosporine, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, More', 'Mometasone furoate, Umeclidinium, Aclidinium, Glycopyrronium, Ipratropium, Cromoglicic acid, Revefenacin, Nedocromil, Tiotropium, Beclomethasone dipropionate, Mupirocin, More', 1767369485);
